    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ContainerAllocator, RMHeartbeatHandler, org.apache.hadoop.service.Service, org.apache.hadoop.yarn.event.EventHandler<ContainerAllocatorEvent>

    public class LocalContainerAllocator
extends RMCommunicator
implements ContainerAllocator
    Allocates containers locally. Doesn't allocate a real container; instead sends an allocated event for all requests.
